// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0175 — Mass File Rename (brotherhood)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 2dd5cc70-655e-5347-bd55-eed3c46683f3

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
